<div style="padding: 20px;">
	<h3 style="text-align: center;font-weight:700;">删除早期上传的视频文件</h3>
	<h4>当前系统最早上传视频的时间是：<span style="font-weight: 700;"> <%= @t_record_info_first_create.created_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S") %></span>  </h4>
	<h4>当前系统最近上传视频的时间是：<span style="font-weight: 700;"> <%= @t_record_info_last_create.created_at.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S") %></span>  </h4>
	<hr>
	<h4 style="color:red;font-weight:700;">一旦提交，此前视频将被彻底删除！务必核对好时间再删：</h4>
	<div style="font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">确定删除:</div>
	<%= form_tag delete_viedo_path,method: :delete do %>
	  <div style="font-weight:700;">
	  	<select name="year">
		  	<% @years.each do |year| %>
		  	  <option value="<%= year %>"><%= year %></option>
		  	<% end %>
		  </select>年
		  <select name="month">
		  	<% @months.each do |month| %>
		  	  <option value="<%= month %>"><%= month %></option>
		  	<% end %>
		  </select>月
		  <select name="day">
		  	<% @days.each do |day| %>
		  	  <option value="<%= day %>"><%= day %></option>
		  	<% end %>
		  </select>日之前的所有视频 <br>
	  </div>
	  
	  <div style="margin-top:30px;"><%= submit_tag "确认提交",data: {disable_with: "提交中..."},class: "btn btn-primary" %></div>
	  
	<% end %>


</div>